 R←Test_Misc_04(stopFlag batchFlag);⎕IO;⎕ML;⎕TRAP;parms;rc;msg;ref;filename
⍝ Send an email with a single attachment: a PDF file
 ⎕IO←1 ⋄ ⎕ML←1
 ⎕TRAP←(999 'C' '. ⍝ Deliberate error')(0 'N')
 R←T._Failed

 parms←⎕NS''
 parms.To←∆SERVER.Userid
 parms.CC←∆TO
 parms.Subj←'From Dyalog SMTP: ',⊃⎕SI
 parms.Body←'Simple text'
 parms.Body,←⎕UCS 13 10
 filename←'./Files/APL-Code.pdf'
 parms.Attachments←⊂filename'application/pdf'
 (rc msg ref)←∆SERVER ##.SendMail parms
 Assert 0=rc

 :If ∆ConfirmEmailOkay'(check the attachment: is a PDF file)'
     R←T._OK
 :EndIf
⍝Done
